<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, July 24 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 4,270 on Friday, down 95.56 points,
or 2.20 percent from that on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover stood at over 62 trillion Turkish Liras (270
million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down sharply by losing 187.26 points,
or 3.48 percent, to close at 5,239.14 points and the industrial
index went down by losing 23.08 points, or 0.62 points, to close
at 3,653.18 points from Thursday's finishes.
</P>
<P>
But the service index closed at 5,046.76, up 27.61 points,
or 0.55 percent, from Thursday's closing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
