<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Rebounds </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, July 24 (Xinhua) -- After continuous declines last week,
the Tunis Stock Exchange index rebounded on Friday to close at
451.41 points, up by 1.29 points compared with that of Thursday's
close.
</P>
<P>
A total of 22,078 shares changed hands and the value hit
535,811 dinars (461,900 U.S. dollars) through 204 turns, in
contrast to 37,529 shares, 7,080,463 dinars (about 6,104,000
dollars) and 327 turns on Thursday, the daily bulletin of the
exchange said. 
</P>
