Murad, MILF vice chairman for military affairs, that a kidnapped
city trader was recently transferred by his captors to another
group of kidnap gang.
</P>
<P>
The MILF has earlier vowed to also neutralize kidnap-for-ransom
groups in Central Mindanao. The military, however, alleged that
the Moro organization is just using updates on kidnapping
activities here for one of its "propagandas."
</P>
<P>
Bautista vowed to launch a massive military operation against
kidnap syndicates operating in the southern Philippines. 
