<TEXT>
<P>
BAGHDAD, July 25 (Xinhua) -- A car bomb exploded Friday night
in the parking lot of the five-star Rasheed hotel here, but nobody
was injured, the Iraqi News Agency reported Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The agency quoted a spokesman for the Ministry of Information
and Culture as saying that the explosion occurred at 9:55
p.m. local time (17:55 GMT). A black Fiyat of 1977 model, full of
