Cup under his helm, another coach should take his place to prepare
for the European Championship qualification rounds.
</P>
<P>
So far, the Santrac's resignation was not yet accepted by the Yugoslavian
Football Association and it was also unclear whether Antic was willing to
overtake the national squad.
