was to secure the implementation of the truce during the games and
maintain its momentum throughout the new millennium.
</P>
<P>
During Athens' bid to host the 2004 games, Greece pledged to
help revive the Olympic truce as an effective mechanism for the
cessation of conflicts and the promotion of peace.
